## ───────────── Secrets & credentials (NEVER commit) ─────────────
# Real secrets go in `dotnet user-secrets` (dev) or environment variables / GitHub Secrets (prod/CI),
# NOT in committed appsettings files. Keep appsettings*.json with PLACEHOLDERS only.
secrets.json
appsettings.*.local.json
appsettings.Local.json
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.pfx
*.p12
*.key
*.pem

## ───────────── Local data / uploads / logs ─────────────
# Local file uploads (FileStorage local provider)
wwwroot/uploads/
uploads/
**/App_Data/
# Local dev databases (SQLite / LocalDB)
*.db
*.db-shm
*.db-wal
*.sqlite
*.mdf
*.ldf
# Logs (Serilog file sink, Seq exports)
logs/
*.log

